snippet.title: Trailer Public Alpha - Blood Arena
snippet.description: Fight in the Blood Arena for your life. Earn, bet money and prove to your team your skills in a fair fight. (3v3, 2v2, 1v1) Blood Arena, poker and many more  activities on Project RED will allow you to earn $EGLD while showing your skills to the whole mafia.
